@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}

### Listar vehículos
GET {{host}}/api/vehiculos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear vehículo
POST {{host}}/api/vehiculos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Toyota",
  "modelo": "Hilux",
  "patente": "AA123BB",
  "año": 2020,
  "capacidad_carga": 1200
}

### Obtener vehículo por id
GET {{host}}/api/vehiculos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar vehículo
PUT {{host}}/api/vehiculos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Toyota",
  "modelo": "Hilux SRV",
  "patente": "AA123BB",
  "año": 2021,
  "capacidad_carga": 1250
}

### Eliminar vehículo
DELETE {{host}}/api/vehiculos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
